DISCLAIMER — SCOPE OF USE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

ADS-B Secure is a research and educational prototype developed for academic
purposes. It is NOT certified for operational aeronautical use and MUST NOT
be used in any safety-critical aviation context.

The HMAC verification component operates exclusively on simulated or
pre-processed data and does not modify, extend, or interfere with the
real ADS-B radio protocol as defined by ICAO Annex 10 and DO-260B.

The system operates in receive-only mode. It does not transmit ADS-B
signals under any circumstances.

Use of this software for offensive purposes, interference with real
aeronautical systems, or any application that violates applicable
aeronautical regulations is strictly prohibited.
